TITLE: Initializing Claim Checker Manager in spomky-labs/jose
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to set up and use the CheckerManager in the spomky-labs/jose library. It includes adding various claim checkers and checking a JWS.
SOURCE: https://github.com/web-token/jwt-doc/blob/v1.x/migration/from-spomky-labs-jose/claim-checking.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
<?php

use Jose\Checker\CheckerManager;
use Jose\Checker\ExpirationTimeChecker;
use Jose\Checker\IssuedAtChecker;
use Jose\Checker\NotBeforeChecker;

$checkerManager = new CheckerManager();
$checkerManager->addClaimChecker(new ExpirationTimeChecker());
$checkerManager->addClaimChecker(new IssuedAtChecker());
$checkerManager->addClaimChecker(new NotBeforeChecker());

$checkerManager->checkJWS($jws, $signature_index);
```

